    "Two such projects are the subject of evaluation in this paper -referred to as P roj A and P roj B in the paper.",
    "P roj A refers to a project in LIEF POST related to the application and recalculation of valueadded tax (VAT or Umsatzsteuer / USt.",
    "in German) for specific regions with special VAT arrangements.",
    "P roj B deals with automated pre-sorting of posts before delivery for an efficient delivery process.",
    "The requirements for most projects in LIEF POST, including P roj A and P roj B, are specified bilingually -a mix of German and English."
  ],
